Beach view



Diana deliberately avoided giving me a different kind of view, of the topless women on the beach.
Sandor Fékété (happily married) tells me the men are also interesting to watch -- the town is known as a gay meeting place.
Taken Friday, September 14, 2001, 12:12:41pm.  Original image size: 1600x1200, 985kb
Technical details: Olympus C700UZ, 1/500s @ F6.3, ISO 100, 86mm
